      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a collector-grade E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This powerhouse achieves its peak output at an 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a lightning-fast M-DCT dual-clutch transmission. The mechanical integrity is absolute, with a documented service history ensuring the rod bearings and throttle actuators are in peak operational state. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a Variable M Differential Lock for surgical cornering precision. This vehicle retains its factory-spec rigidity and aerodynamic profile, presented in concours-level condition with zero aftermarket modifications. A true purist\u2019s specimen.",
